        Creates an instance of HasSizeMatcher which checks size of an instance of SearchContext. It should be WebElement or some implementor of HasSize or WrapsElement. Otherwise the matching returns false.
        Type Parameters:
        T - is a type of a value to be matched. It should extend WebElement or it should extend both SearchContext and HasSize.

        width - expected width of the element
        height - expected height of the element
